<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xl-12">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-xl-4">
        <div class="oval-shaped-graphic">
          <div id="servicesImagesCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li data-target="#servicesImagesCarousel" data-slide-to='0' class="active"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active image text-center">
                <%= link_to services_path do %>
                  <%= image_tag 'services.png', class: 'rounded-circle', width: '350px', height: '250px' %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#servicesImagesCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>

            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#servicesImagesCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="oval-text text-center mt-5 mb-5">
            greenGoat offers tax advantaged redistribution, but also â€¦ consulting, specification writing, recycling reports and more!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-xl-4">
        <div class="oval-shaped-graphic">
          <div id="buyImagesCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li data-target="#buyImagesCarousel" data-slide-to='0' class="active"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active image text-center">
                <%= link_to items_path do %>
                  <%= image_tag 'buy.png', class: 'rounded-circle', width: '350px', height: '250px' %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#buyImagesCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>

            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#buyImagesCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="oval-text text-center mt-5 mb-5">
            greenGoat resells residential materials old and new. A lot of our materials come from very well maintained home, and sell for a fraction of their retail value!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-xl-4">
        <div class="oval-shaped-graphic">

          <div id="projectImagesCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li data-target="#projectImagesCarousel" data-slide-to='0' class="active"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active image text-center">
                <%= link_to calculate_worth_path do %>
                  <%= image_tag 'donate.png', class: 'rounded-circle', width: '350px', height: '250px' %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#projectImagesCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>

            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#projectImagesCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="oval-text text-center mt-5 mb-5">
            For homeowners about to rebuild, donate unwanted materials to greenGoat! We work in parallel with the design and permitting process, so there is no delay in construction.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <br>
  <div class="row mt-5">
    <%= render 'sidebar' %>

    <div class="col-8 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xl-10">
      <div class="page-title mb-4">
        <h1>greenGoat mission</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="intro lightgray-background p-4 border-radius-15">
        <p>greenGoat facilitates evolutionary resource management (from our beginnings in salvaging and recycling construction and demolition - 'C&D' - debris to our current concentration in residential projects).</p>
        <p>We handle everything from material placement, removal (for full demo projects), hauling storage, and reporting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
